flowchart LR
    A[Request or external event] --> B[Create run_id]
    B --> C[(Append run.started)]
    C --> D[Feature intake]

    D --> E{Intent clear?}
    E -- No --> F[awaiting_confirmation]
    F --> F1[(Persist waiting_on: human)]
    F1 --> F2{Human response}
    F2 -- Confirm --> G
    F2 -- Cancel --> X[cancelled]
    E -- Yes --> G{Assign lane}

    G -- Tiny --> H[Feature branch]
    G -- Normal --> I[Isolated worktree]
    G -- High-risk --> J[Brainstorm → Research → Plan]
    J --> I
    H --> K[implementing]
    I --> K

    K --> L[Implement]
    L --> M[Spec review]
    M --> N[Quality review]
    N --> O[Correctness review]
    O --> P[Intent review]
    P --> Q[verifying]
    Q --> R{Verification passes?}
    R -- Yes --> S[Commit and push]
    R -- No --> RF

    S --> T[awaiting_ci]
    T --> U{CI result}
    U -- Pass --> V[awaiting_review]
    U -- Fail --> RF

    V --> W{Reviewer event}
    W -- Approved --> Y[ready_to_merge]
    W -- Changes requested --> RF
    Y --> Z{Landed SHA confirmed?}
    Z -- Yes --> SH[shipped]
    Z -- No --> RF
    SH --> BK[Post-merge bookkeeping]

    subgraph RECOVERY[Bounded recovery]
        RF[Operation failure] --> L1[L1 deterministic repair]
        L1 --> V1{External validation passes?}
        V1 -- Yes --> RES[Resume prior workflow state]
        V1 -- No --> L2[L2 constrained agent repair]
        L2 --> RB{Retry budget remains?}
        RB -- Yes --> ATT[One bounded attempt]
        ATT --> VAL[Re-run real operation]
        VAL --> OK{Ground truth passes?}
        OK -- Yes --> RES
        OK -- No --> SIG{Repeated failure?}
        SIG -- No --> L2
        SIG -- Yes --> ESC[escalated]
        RB -- No --> ESC
        ESC --> TRAIL[(Persist attempt trail and resume event)]
        TRAIL --> HUM[Operator decision]
        HUM -- Retry --> L1
        HUM -- Resume with changed scope --> RES
        HUM -- Stop --> BLK[blocked or cancelled]
    end

    RES -. verification repaired .-> Q
    RES -. CI repaired .-> T
    RES -. review addressed .-> V
    RES -. push repaired .-> Y

    X --> END((Terminal))
    BLK --> END
    BK --> END
